00:35:18.540 --> 00:35:21.510
that no one else has before.

00:35:21.510 --> 00:35:23.070
And the biggest
thing is you just

00:35:23.070 --> 00:35:25.440
have to get out there
and start trying things.

00:35:25.440 --> 00:35:29.040
So many brands want
to just sit there

00:35:29.040 --> 00:35:32.350
and wait for the perfect
opportunity to come along.

00:35:32.350 --> 00:35:35.460
But the thing is, is
that, if someone else has,

00:35:35.460 --> 00:35:38.072
or if you're looking
for a case study that--

00:35:38.072 --> 00:35:39.280
I think Seth Godin said this.

00:35:39.280 --> 00:35:42.120
If you're looking for
a case study that's

00:35:42.120 --> 00:35:43.590
come out about what
you want to do,

00:35:43.590 --> 00:35:45.840
chances are you're going to
be too late at that point,

00:35:45.840 --> 00:35:48.420
because you're just going
to be the "me too" person.

00:35:48.420 --> 00:35:50.125
You're going to be
that brand that's

00:35:50.125 --> 00:35:53.420
jut saying something that
someone else has already said.

